oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Campus, circa 1965
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Aerial photograph of campus, circa 1965. "As MTSC days drew to a close, the campus had more buildings and more students than ever before. By 1965, enrollment reached 6,000 and many recently constructed buildings dotted the landscape" (from Barnett, Holly, et al. Middle Tennessee State University. College History Series. Charleston, SC: Arcadia, 2001. p. 92).
